title: New Orleans Saints vs. Dallas Cowboys: Live in-game chat, updates
text:
The New Orleans Saints will welcome the return of quarterback Drew Brees and hope to avoid an 0-4 start to the 2015 season when they face the Dallas Cowboys at the Mercedes-Benz Superdome.
The game kicks off at 7:30 p.m. Central time and will be televised by NBC (WDSU locally). Further TV information is here .
The Saints (0-3) have lost six games in a row at the Superdome, while the Cowboys (2-1) have won 10 consecutive games on the road.
Saints beat writers Katherine Terrell and Evan Woodbery , managing producer Christopher Dabe and columnists Larry Holder and Jeff Duncan will be on hand for live updates. Your thoughts are welcome in the comments section below.
